Typography

Font Family

•
Primary Font: Inter. This sans-serif font was chosen for its exceptional readability and clean, modern aesthetic. It ensures that all communication is clear and accessible, directly addressing the target user’s feeling of being overwhelmed by complexity. It feels professional and trustworthy without being intimidating.

•
Secondary Font: DM Serif Display. This serif font was chosen for major headlines to convey a sense of authority, quality, and pride. Its elegant and sophisticated character helps elevate the brand, assuring the business owner that the final product will be something they are proud to share.

